race.comment: MISS CAPRICORN (11) made the perfect return at Orange when running away from them. Left herself with too much to do last time but finished full of running. Peaking now and draws well again. Leading player. ll. TIGER TOWN (3) drops back in trip off 34 days and strikes a much more suitable assignment back on the country circuit. Has trialled well in between runs and looms a serious threat. NOR NOR WEST (10) proved too sharp for MISS CAPRICORN last time at Dubbo to make it two on the trot. However, concedes weight to her now and is drawn far less kind. Keeping in mind. SHADDAP (8) sets up nicely for this third-up off two solid hitouts. Should blend into the race nicely from his middle draw and is worth considering.
